Added detailed `rationale` attribute to every non-Ragas metric class (7 operational + 2 knowledge) and exposed it in `raki metrics --json` output. Added new `docs/metrics/rationale-and-interpretation.md` with per-metric design rationale, interpretation tables, pitfall warnings, and combined metric pattern analysis. Cross-referenced from `docs/metrics/operational.md`, `docs/metrics/knowledge.md`, and `docs/interpretation-reference.md`.
